msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cuser-guide%5Chr-onboarding.md:3
msgid ""
"From v2.4.0, the RONL Business API caseworker dashboard includes an **HR "
"onboarding flow** that lets HR staff start, track, and complete a structured "
"employee onboarding process entirely within MijnOmgeving. The process is "
"backed by the `HrOnboardingProcess` BPMN and the `EmployeeRoleAssignment` "
"DMN, using the same claim-first caseworker task queue as the AWB "
"Kapvergunning."
msgstr ""

